				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-kh%C3%A1n-s%C6%A1n/poem-lPXitS2M9bnMrPhncY5fkQ">Giang thượng khán sơn - 江上看山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-C%C3%A1n/H%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-lang-T%E1%BB%91ng-H%E1%BB%93-Bang-H%C3%A0nh-%C4%91%C3%A3i-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3-T%C3%A2n-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-nQw0oOi1cLfnsJ3Wb8gufg">Hạ tân lang - Tống Hồ Bang Hành đãi chế phó Tân Châu - 賀新郎－送胡邦衡待制赴新州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-C%C3%A1n/author-XtDwgc81LrI5SWqmLkXQ1Q">Trương Nguyên Cán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/K%C3%BD-Kho%C3%A1i-Ch%C3%A2u-ph%E1%BB%A7-ph%E1%BB%A7-t%C3%A1-Cao-X%C3%A1-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-7U6SWhlrhO2OhgalvTtvxg">Ký Khoái Châu phủ phủ tá Cao Xá hữu nhân - 寄快州府府佐高舍友人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/Qu%C3%A1-C%E1%BB%95-Phao-th%C3%A0nh/poem-O2JhxpQpFO6IgltfbmNGGA">Quá Cổ Phao thành - 過古拋城</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-%C3%81n/author-7tg_rhleFYVL5Ann2EB2iA">Trần Danh Án</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Ti%C3%AAu-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Khanh-th%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A1n/poem--LsKiQ1eOygSMk7fNhUr8w">Tiêu Trọng Khanh thê - Đệ nhị đoạn - 焦仲卿妻－第二段</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/T%C3%BAc-H%E1%BA%ADu-L%E1%BB%99c-d%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-byzvzbeaWBZT9yvqA8_Cyw">Túc Hậu Lộc dạ vũ hữu cảm - 宿厚祿夜雨有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-ioE9gUDRRK0CF1f-0I-Dgw">Châu Hải Đường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/T%C6%B0-Dung-h%E1%BA%A3i-m%C3%B4n/poem-sHLcz-FU0JUhqAYIoPW1lQ">Tư Dung hải môn - 思容海門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/author-AYxqc_FV5QBUSOHCh_p6ZA">Nguyễn Anh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%B1-khuy%E1%BA%BFn/poem-OI5-ujXRpOZC6BRiidHQuw">Tự khuyến - 自勸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/T%E1%BB%AD-quy/poem-BZtVKAu5IOR41L5TXLK3Fw">Tử quy - 子規</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/author-qoi_3MEdeZkoj0TClsekFA">Ngô Dung</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
